                <div class="illus-type-body">
                  <div class="illus-type-name">Low-fi workflow UI</div>
                  <div class="illus-type-desc">Simplified UI mockups for complex system explanations. Avoid real screen-within-screen screenshots.</div>
                  <div class="illus-type-sub">Use for</div>
                  <ul class="illus-type-list">
                    <li>Guided onboarding</li>
                    <li>AI remediation walkthroughs</li>
                    <li>Spotlight tours &middot; Feature education</li>
                    <li>Multi-step deployment explanation</li>
                    <li>Automation flow previews</li>
                    <li>Tree navigation tutorials</li>
                  </ul>
                  <div class="illus-type-sub">Rules</div>
                  <ul class="illus-type-list">
                    <li>Use neutral gray UI blocks</li>
                    <li>Sharp corners for structural clarity</li>
                    <li>Simplified component shapes</li>
                    <li>No realistic screenshots</li>
                    <li>No exact UI replication</li>
                    <li>Highlight only the learning concept</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>

